  "title": "Senior / Therapy Assistant",
  "description": "<p>The incumbent is responsible to:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assist in helping patients on use of therapeutic equipment</li>\n  <li>Assist in supervising patients in the performing of therapeutic activities, assessments, caregiver training, or interventions</li>\n  <li>Maintain general cleanliness, tidiness and infection control of the therapy area</li>\n  <li>Perform daily equipment checks and maintenance</li>\n  <li>Perform daily inventory checking and bi-yearly inventory stock take</li>\n  <li>Monitor consumables levels on a daily basis</li>\n  <li>Assist in admin tasks e.g. handling enquiries, filing and data entry</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum O/N Level with WSQ Certificate in Therapy Services, or NITEC in Community Care &amp; Social Services</li>\n  <li>Experience in a healthcare setting will be an advantage</li>\n  <li>Possess patient-centredness and interpersonal skills</li>\n</ul>",
